column2: SELECT     fGetNearbyObjEq(#.,#.,#.* #) n, P.objid ,P.ra,P.dec,dered_r,dered_i,dered_g,cmodelmag_i,extinction_i,fiber2mag_i, s.z, s.velDisp, pz.z as photoz, pz.zErr as photozerr FROM    fGetNearbyObjEq(#.,#.,#.* #) n   JOIN photoprimary as P on n.objID = p.objID    JOIN dr1#..SpecObj as S on P.objid = S. bestObjID   JOIN PhotoZ as pz on P.objid = pz.objid WHERE  (dered_r-dered_i) <  # AND (dered_r-dered_i) > # AND (dered_g-dered_r) <  # AND (dered_g-dered_r) > # AND (cmodelmag_i-extinction_i) BETWEEN # AND # AND   fiber2mag_i < # AND   AND s.z < #   AND s.velDisp > #. INTO micado_galaxies_loRG_rho_#_#
